name: Teriyaki Sesame Salmon
description: Fresh Atlantic salmon marinated in a savory teriyaki sauce and topped with toasted sesame seeds. Oven-baked to perfection.

name: Honey Chipotle Salmon
description: Salmon glazed with a sweet and smoky honey chipotle sauce. Grilled for a slightly charred flavor.

name: Lemon Herb Crusted Sea Bass
description: Sustainable sea bass coated in a zesty lemon and herb crust. Pan-seared for a crispy exterior and flaky interior.

name: Garlic & Herb Tilapia
description: Mild tilapia seasoned with a blend of garlic, herbs, and spices. Baked for a light and flavorful option.

name: Cajun Shrimp & Andouille Sausage
description: Plump shrimp and spicy andouille sausage simmered in a flavorful Cajun sauce. Served over creamy grits.

name: Blackened Mahi Mahi
description: Mahi mahi seasoned with a blackened spice blend and seared for a bold and delicious flavor.

name: Shrimp Scampi with Linguine
description: Tender shrimp sauteed in garlic, butter, white wine, and lemon juice. Served over linguine pasta.

name: Pan-Seared Scallops with Risotto
description: Large, seared scallops served over creamy Parmesan risotto.

name: Tuscan White Bean & Tuna Stew
description: Hearty stew with flaked tuna, white beans, tomatoes, and fresh herbs. Perfect for a comforting meal.

name: Sesame Seed Ahi Tuna Poke Bowl
description: Marinated ahi tuna cubes served over sushi rice with various toppings like avocado, seaweed salad, and pickled ginger.

name: Salmon Nigiri
description: Slices of fresh salmon nigiri sushi served with pickled ginger and wasabi.

name: California Roll
description: Classic California roll with imitation crab, avocado, and cucumber inside, and tobiko on top.
